title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - What's new in the marketplace - week 28
description:
In this video we will look at this weeks addition to the marketplace for MSFS 2020. This week I think we almost hit a record: 53 new items have been added to the marketplace. The updates include both livery packs, scenery enhancement, missions packs and update airports. Unfortunately no new aircrafts have been added.
